            "markup": "<p><strong data-start=\"516\" data-end=\"548\">Send an inquiry via the form</strong><br>Provide basic information about the project, and our team will contact you with a proposed solution.</p><p data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"770\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"><strong data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"675\">A response within 24 hours</strong><br>After receiving your inquiry, you will get feedback and the next steps for carrying out the project.</p>"
